@startuml WorkshopActivityPhases
title Workshop Activity Phases (SMD-06)
hide empty description

state "Setup Phase" as setup_phase
note right of setup_phase
Instructor edits settings, grading 
strategy (rubric), and instructions. 
Students cannot submit yet. 
end note

state "Submission Phase" as submission_phase
note right of submission_phase
Students can upload their work. They 
cannot assess others yet. 
end note

state "Assessment Phase" as assessment_phase
note right of assessment_phase
Submissions are closed. Students are 
allocated peers (randomly or manually) 
and must grade them using the rubric. 
end note

state "Grading Evaluation Phase" as grading_evaluation_phase
note right of grading_evaluation_phase
Peer assessments are finished. The 
system calculates grades based on the 
grading strategy. The Instructor reviews 
scores and can override them. 
end note

state "Closed" as closed
note right of closed
Grades are pushed to the Gradebook. 
Students can see their grades and the 
feedback they received. 
end note

setup_phase --> submission_phase : Instructor Switches Phase
submission_phase --> assessment_phase : Instructor Switches Phase
assessment_phase --> grading_evaluation_phase : Instructor Switches Phase
grading_evaluation_phase --> closed : Instructor Switches Phase

@enduml
